-----------------------------------------------------------------
Solyaris - A Visual Movie Browser
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Solyaris is an exploration into organic information design to 
visualise movies, actors, directors and their relationship. 

Search the entire Open Movie Database (TMDb) collection for 
movies, actors or directors. Expand nodes to gather information 
about their connections. Learn about the cast and filmography. 

All information courtesy of TMDb, IMDb and Wikipedia. This product 
uses the TMDb API but is not endorsed or certified by The Open 
Movie Database or any other third party.

Made with Cinder.


Project URL:
http://solyaris.cecinestpasparis.net

App Store:
http://itunes.apple.com/app/solyaris-a-visual-movie-browser/id481963410?mt=8



